profile:
“Awaken to a space tailored to reflect your lifestyle. Kitchens designs start with inspiration. Our showroom is the perfect place to view beautiful cabinetry.”
Your cabinetry is the largest piece of furniture in your home and is a reflection of your personal taste and style. 
Ekko Cabinetry will provide the attention to detail that your project deserves. 
Ask about our products with a lifetime warranty.
Ekko Cabinetry is open for business and is following all Covid protocols.
Check us out on INSTAGRAM. www.instagram.com/ekkocabinetry/?hl=en
hours: Monday to Friday 9am - 5pm.Saturday 10am-3pm. Closed on Long Weekends.

We work directly with home owners, contractors and builders to provide high quality, affordable, custom cabinetry.
